OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,FA homeless alcoholic has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor killing a former head chef, who
OL,8,Fwas also homeless and suffering from
OL,9,Faddiction.
OL,11,FAdam Rowson, 26, beat Alexis De Naray,
OL,12,Fleaving him dead or dying in an
OL,13,Fabandoned garage in Shrewsbury in June
OL,14,F2025. He then used the 45-year-old's
OL,15,Fbank card to buy alcohol and
OL,16,Fscratchcards.
OL,18,FRowson, of no fixed address, has been
OL,19,Fjailed for at least 16 years for
OL,20,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
