FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,FThe court heard Rowson and Mr De Naray
OL,7,Fhad met at the Royal Shrewsbury
OL,8,FHospital in the early hours of June 24
OL,9,Flast year.
OL,11,FRowon then offered his victim, who was
OL,12,Falso an alcoholic, a place to stay for
OL,13,Fone night.
OL,15,FHe left Mr De Naray, who studied at
OL,16,FLeiths School of Food and Wine and had
OL,17,Fpreviously worked at Claridge's, with
OL,18,Fa traumatic brain injury and 20 rib
OL,19,Ffractures, three of which occurred
OL,20,Fafter his death, and multiple injuries
OL,21,Fto his head, torso and upper limbs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement,
OL,7,FAlexandros De Naray said his older
OL,8,Fbrother was "one of the most caring
OL,9,Fand loving people I have ever known".
OL,11,FHe said: "He was my best friend I
OL,12,Floved him more than I could ever
OL,13,Fexplain...
OL,15,F"I think every day how I can never see
OL,16,Fhim again and one of the people I
OL,17,Floved most in the world has been taken
OL,18,Faway from me in such a horrible way.
OL,26,@pD@MOUqD@dO]sD@JOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,F"I can only hope he felt no pain in
OL,7,Fhis last moments and he is now at
OL,8,Fpeace.
OL,10,F"I just hope everyone remembers he was
OL,11,Fa kind and loving person who meant so
OL,12,Fmuch to us and will always been in our
OL,13,Fmemories every day."
OL,15,FHis father Constantine De Naray said
OL,16,Fhis son was "funny, kind, thoughtful,
OL,17,Fgenerous and a loving son".
OL,19,FHe said: "My wonderful boy did not
OL,20,Fdeserve to lose his life... He was a
OL,21,Fdear son who we will forever miss.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@TO]xD@MOUyD@ZO]{D@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
