PN,37405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,F"He was a very talented chef who
OL,7,Fworked in London until he became
OL,8,Funwell and moved to Shrewsbury to be
OL,9,Fclose to family.
OL,11,F"He was gradually getting better when
OL,12,Fhe sadly lost his life. No parent
OL,13,Fshould have to bury a child, more
OL,14,Fespecially in these horrendous
OL,15,Fcircumstances."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
