OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,FJailing him for life at Stafford Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Wednesday, Judge Avik
OL,8,FMukherjee said Rowson knew he had
OL,9,Fkilled Mr De Naray when he "callously"
OL,10,Fused his card and "freely spent his
OL,11,Fmoney on anything that pleased you"
OL,12,Funtil he was stopped by the bank.
OL,14,FJudge Mukherjee said: "By the time you
OL,15,Fleft him in the disused garage,
OL,16,Fprobably on the 25th June, he had been
OL,17,Fso severely beaten by you he was dying
OL,18,For dead.
OL,26,@qD@\OUqD@fO]rD@SOUsD@cO]vD@WOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,F"You left him in that physical state.
OL,7,FRather than calling for help, you left
OL,8,Fhim to die. You covered his body...
OL,9,Fbecause you knew what you had done to
OL,10,Fhim."
OL,12,FRowson also threw away a T-shirt he
OL,13,Fhad been wearing, which the judge said
OL,14,Fshowed how "forensically astute your
OL,15,Fthinking was at the time".
OL,17,FRowson allegedly told a friend: "Have
OL,18,Fyou heard about the situation, it got
OL,19,Fbad bro, I don't even want to go home
OL,20,Fbecause I think I killed someone."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@EO]vD@LOUwD@YO]yD@aOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,FThe judge added: "You lied to the
OL,7,Femergency services, you lied to police
OL,8,Fat the scene.
OL,10,F"Only you know the full detail of what
OL,11,Fyou did. I'm sure you have not told
OL,12,Fthe truth at any stage about the
OL,13,Fassault on Alexis."
OL,15,FThe defendant, who wore glasses and a
OL,16,Fblue T-shirt with a collar in the
OL,17,Fdock, showed no emotion and nodded his
OL,18,Fhead as the judge handed down his
OL,19,Fsentence.
OL,26,@nD@ROUrD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
