OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1778091067
OL,3,CAlcoholic jailed for beating former
OL,4,Chead chef to death
OL,6,FDefending, Michelle Heeley KC said
OL,7,FRowson was sorry and that alcohol and
OL,8,Fdrugs had contributed "significantly"
OL,9,Fto what he had done.
OL,11,FShe said: "Through me he would like to
OL,12,Fapologise... he recognises the pain he
OL,13,Fhas caused the family.
OL,15,F"He is still a relatively young man,
OL,16,F26 now and not particularly mature.
OL,17,FWhile in custody he has found a job...
OL,18,Fhe is trying to pay his debt in some
OL,19,Fminor way. The structure has
OL,20,Fbenefitted him.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@eO]sD@KOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
